      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/b/e9a140/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2025-02-04T15:43:37.332Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi, I am still having this issue happen to me. I was doing a 1.5 hour ride on Sunday and the app started loosing connection with my Tacx neo 2t trainer every minute or so it the last 15 minutes of my workout. I would basically close the app, restart it, continue and then it would work for a minute or so and then happen again. As you can imagine it was quite annoying having to watch the app constantly for when it would drop out of connection and quickly pause the workout, restart it and try and continue.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/794725d07fae04d057b9d3c9c27b4436b793a14a.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/794725d07fae04d057b9d3c9c27b4436b793a14a\" title=\"IMG_4576\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/794725d07fae04d057b9d3c9c27b4436b793a14a_2_231x500.png\" alt=\"IMG_4576\" data-base62-sha1=\"hiScQsy6pnvCv2NRSowvySCCqTw\" width=\"231\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/794725d07fae04d057b9d3c9c27b4436b793a14a_2_231x500.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/794725d07fae04d057b9d3c9c27b4436b793a14a_2_346x750.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/794725d07fae04d057b9d3c9c27b4436b793a14a_2_462x1000.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"2A2E3B\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_4576</span><span class=\"informations\">1170\u00d72532 164 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/c/c9c4396c18655476920602aa628acfa69b721c1e.jpeg\