      "created_at": "2025-02-04T16:02:44.743Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I have a 2T but I am using my spin bike and too lazy / old to spend that much time in the cold on my 2T\u2026 I should ask what phone do you have here?  Looks like iPhone\u2026  which model out of curiosity.  I should say it\u2019s possible this is related to your device or some interference or something but it\u2019s so strange I am slightly leading towards something in our app but since you are the only one with this issue it\u2019s hard to say.</p>",
