      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/f/b782af/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2025-03-29T03:02:01.751Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I encountered this issue for the first time today. App version 5.2.2, iOS 18.4, erg mode, Wahoo Kickr Core, Power Match on with dual-sided crank arm power meter. Been using the app since September 2023 without a problem.</p>\n<p>Maybe six or eight times in an hour long workout power would rapidly ramp down and then stabilize ~25% below the setpoint (225\u2013&gt;160ish). Each time I was able to immediately kick the app back into control by increasing erg % up and then down or by toggling into slope mode then back into erg mode.</p>",
